Texts.Chs: 在^orange;黑暗发展部堡垒^reset;中找到^orange;造物^reset;
Texts.Eng: Find the ^orange;artifact^reset; in the ^orange;Dark Miniknog stronghold^reset;

Texts.Chs: 列表上的下一个项目是抽猴子。好吧，不是那种。去杀一只大猴子。
Texts.Eng: Next on da list, smacking da monkey. Okay, not that kind. Go kill a Big Ape.

Texts.Chs: 好吧，喵现在真的非常担心。来自凯文的新信息。“我的错。都是我的错。都是我的错。”很不像他。但他又做错了什么呢？
Texts.Eng: Okay, mew is really really concerned now. New Kevin message. "My fault. All my fault. ALL MY FAULT." Very unlike him. What his fault though?

Texts.Chs: 回到^orange;科学前哨站^reset;去找^orange;溪^reset;
